        <updateDate>2007-12-04T21:22:31Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Atomic Veterans Medal Act of 2007 - Directs the Secretary of Defense to: (1) design and produce an Atomic Testing Service Medal to honor members of the Armed Forces who were exposed to ionizing radiation as a result of U.S. atomic weapons tests conducted between 1945 and 1963; and (2) issue the Medal to such individuals (or their next-of-kin).</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Atomic Veterans Medal Act of 2007</title>
    <titles>
